[38;5;141m> [0mNow I have a solid understanding of the structure, style, and content needed. Let me write the Python companion for Recipe 7.4 (ED Visit Prediction). This will use SageMaker for model training/hosting and demonstrate a gradient boosted tree approach for predicting ED visits.[0m[0m
